Teewah is a town within the locality of Noosa North Shore in the Shire of Noosa, Queensland, Australia. It is  north of the large city centre of Noosa Heads. It is inaccessible by road. It is a well known camping area and offroad vehicles can drive on the beach.
History
Between 2008 and Teewah, Noosa North Shore (and the rest of the Shire of Noosa) was within Sunshine Coast Region.
